Text: • Frequency of site inspections
Close-out rate of actions
Lagging Indicators (Reactive)
Incidents and near misses
Non-compliances
Enforcement actions
0 Audit failures
Balanced Approach
High-performing organisations prioritise leading indicators while learning from lagging data.
6. Site Vérification Techniques
6.1 Observations
Focus on:
•
Task execution vs documented method
•
Use of controls (PPE, barriers, permits)
Behaviour under pressure
Key question:
"What actually happens when no one is watching?"
6.2 Interviews
Engage with:
0
Operatives
•
Supervisors
Site managers
Ask:
•
•
"Can you explain how you do this task?"
“What would you do if something changed?”
"What are the biggest risks?”

