Ο Documentation vs execution
Ο
Consistency across teams
6.4 Triangulation
Combine:
0
What is written
0
What is said
What is done
Gaps between these indicate risk.
7. Red Flags: Identifying "Paper Compliance"
Key warning signs include:
Documentation Issues
0
Generic, copy-paste method statements
Overly complex or excessively long documents
0
Lack of task-specific risk detail
Operational Disconnect
0
Workforce unaware of SSOW content
0
Controls not implemented in practice
