- Text: • Supervisors relying on experience rather than procedure

Cultural Indicators
• "Tick-box" briefings
• Documentation completed retrospectively
• Resistance to questioning or challenge

Audit Signals
• Perfect paperwork with poor site conditions
0 Repeated findings with no improvement
• High lagging indicators despite “compliance”

