8.1 Lessons Learned
• Capture from:
Ο Audits
Ο Incidents
Ο Near misses
• Feed back into:
Ο SSOW updates
Ο Training
Ο Risk assessments

8.2 Action Management
• Assign clear ownership
• Define realistic deadlines
• Track completion and effectiveness

